        "subject": "LU-3753 osp: prioritize MDS-OST synchronization",
        "message": "LU-3753 osp: prioritize MDS-OST synchronization\n\nthe synchronization should be done in background so\nuse lower priority and reschedule when requested.\n\nthis is a short term workaround, in the long term we\nshould use batching to reduce overhead by few orders\nof magnitude.\n\nSigned-off-by: Alex Zhuravlev <alexey.zhuravlev@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I5387ec79d84cb2798b4c9f68183fece1d1216fa3\n"
